name: Minnie Pant Instretch Twill
description: A little bit '50s, our Minnie pant is chic and slim-fitting (thanks to a flattering two-way stretch fabric), with an exact-right-length cropped leg.

name: Cece Ballet Flats
description: Beautifully styled in sumptuous suede (from Italy, of course) and loaded with design details (so they feel as good as they look), these flats feature a cushioned insole for maximum comfort, a rubber sole and a removed shank for maximum flexibility as well as an elasticized topline so they hug your feet just so. Last but not least, we added an interior wedge so you're not completely one with the ground.

name: Hosiery TIghts
description:
Luxury you can feel on the skin…Super-transparent soft tights with incredibly smooth, matt look.
Excellent stretch and a perfect fit, thanks to the use of double-wrapped elastane in each row
Soft knitted waistband with the Wolford logo
Barely visible shadow toe reinforcement
Cotton gusset

Front button closure.

By BP.; imported.
BP.

          Side zip

Women's Active & Swim.

name: SLIM FLAGSTONE LONG-SLEEVE TEE
description: We crafted this classic tee in an updated version of our slub cotton—an amazingly soft fabric made from twisted yarns of varying widths that are specially woven to produce a slightly textured look and feel. Not your average tee, its unconventional construction creates a unique "high-low" pattern that makes it a wardrobe all-star in any season. Online only.

name: SLIM-STRAIGHT JEAN IN RESIN CRINKLE WASH
description: Looking for our vintage slim-straight fit? It's now called slim-straight. It's the exact same fit you already know and love—the only thing that's changed is the name. We wash these jeans with a special treatment to give them a great crinkled look. Since they're indigo dyed, they're prone to crocking, or color transfer, so wear (and wash) them with dark colors till they're worn in.

name: LEATHER ROLLER-BUCKLE BELT
description: Painstakingly crafted right here in the USA, it's the piece that pulls together every outfit.

name: Desert Boot-Men
description: An international cult classic, the iconic men's Desert® Boot by Clarks Originals® was inspired by crepe-soled boots worn by British officers in World War II. Crafted from natural materials including beeswax leather for supreme comfort, its timeless styling has remained unchanged for over 60 years.

name: BROKEN-IN LONG-SLEEVE TEE
description: Hard washed for softness and a broken-in appearance, this tee looks and feels like the well-worn favorite you had in college. An exceptionally comfortable layering piece that's sharp enough to wear on its own, it's the kind of shirt you can never have too many of.

name: Square Buckle Notched Belt

name: Heritage vintage straight chino

name: Buckley Brogue
description: The Buckley Brogue in bistre is a lace up brogue shoe with classic brogue punch work inspired by a vintage style bought at a London market. This classic style has been constructed using specially sourced leather and designed to provide maximum comfort. Carefully washed and hand burnished for an authentic look, the Buckley Brogue is also available in oxblood and camo .

name: VINTAGE POLO
description: A clean-cut standard that goes with just about anything, the polo has been a men's wardrobe staple for years. We constructed ours from supersoft cotton to handle the nine-to-five and the five-to-nine with ease. Rock washed for comfort and a lived-in look and feel, it's cut slimmer than our classic polo but offers a bit more room than our slim fit.
